![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d92a20e2-f2f8-4066-8bd2-e434c4521b5e/1000006074.jpg?format=original)

This April marks the return of Josiah Power and a new iteration of The Power Company to DC All In with The Power Company: Recharged, and DC is revealing a first look at interior art from issue #1 by Khary Randolph and Alitha Martinez. This DC All In one-shot not only features the return of writer Hill to DC and the return of Josiah Power but brings together a collection of DC Super Heroes – Batman (Jace Fox), Vixen, and Duke Thomas, aka The Signal – to join Black Lightning in fighting anti-metahuman sentiment at the street level (thanks to Amanda Waller and _Absolute Power_).

Spinning out of the events of Black Lightning and DC Power: Rise of the Power Company, Josiah Power and Jefferson Pierce lead the newest iteration of the Power Company with a new purpose of rebuilding humanity’s faith in heroes and fighting back against the rising anti-metahuman movement that Amanda Waller instigated in DC’s Absolute Power.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/26172a62-39fe-4349-bbda-1a060461e2b6/TPC_Recharged+Preview%281%29.jpg?format=original)

Bryan Edward Hill makes his return to DC comics. He recently revitalized Blade for Marvel and is doing a stellar job on Ultimate Black Panther. He brings his talent back to DC to raise the bar for these great heroes. Bryan did a fantastic job with Batman and the Outsiders and now he's back to tackle more characters on the edge of greatness. DC has been ALL IN on many of its heroes in this current era and we cannot wait to see how he elevates these heroes to a new level of prominence and recognition.

For their first mission the Company dispatches Batman (Jace Fox), The Signal, and Vixen to investigate a serial killer that’s been hunting metahumans in the streets of Atlanta.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5509c4ff-d68e-4a9f-924a-9cab965ef082/TPC_Recharged+Preview%282%29.jpg?format=original) ![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/9019d2a3-5893-4f92-af38-97442e0b3a0f/TPC_Recharged+Preview%283%29.jpg?format=original) ![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7d6aa39d-84e7-4c62-a8b1-7f95aeb6fc8f/TPC_Recharged+Preview%284%29.jpg?format=original) ![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b3a789c1-6b72-40cf-b10f-f1b6954ff1b1/TPC_Recharged+Preview%285%29.jpg?format=original)

